graph LR
    NotebookController[Notebook Controller<br/>Kubeflow Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    NotebookController -->|platform| Kubernetes[Kubernetes 1.22.0+]
    NotebookController -->|framework| ControllerRuntime[controller-runtime]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    NotebookController -.->|traffic mgmt<br/>VirtualServices| Istio[Istio]
    NotebookController -.->|metrics| Prometheus[Prometheus]
    NotebookController -.->|build-time only| Kubebuilder[Kubebuilder 3.3.0+]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    NotebookController -->|Go library| CommonUtils[components/common<br/>Shared Utilities]
    NotebookController -.->|routes traffic<br/>when USE_ISTIO=true| IstioGateway[Istio Gateway]

    %% Integration Points (Consumers)
    JupyterWebApp[jupyter-web-app<br/>Kubeflow UI] -->|creates Notebook CRs| NotebookController
    ODHDashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|UI integration| NotebookController

    %% Integration Points (Created Resources)
    NotebookController -->|creates/manages| StatefulSets[StatefulSets<br/>apps/v1]
    NotebookController -->|creates/manages| Services[Services<br/>core/v1]
    NotebookController -.->|creates when<br/>USE_ISTIO=true| VirtualServices[VirtualServices<br/>networking.istio.io]

    %% Managed Resources
    StatefulSets -->|runs| NotebookPods[Notebook Pods<br/>Jupyter Servers]

    %% API Server
    NotebookController -->|watches/manages CRDs| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    JupyterWebApp -->|creates resources| K8sAPI

    %% External Services (accessed by notebooks)
    NotebookPods -.->|model storage| S3[S3 / Object Storage]
    NotebookPods -.->|code repos| Git[Git Repositories]
    NotebookPods -.->|data sources| Databases[Databases]

